===Etymology===
{{zh-ref|Schuessler (2024)}} considers this a {{m|und|*-t}} derivation of {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*nwe||warm}}, whence also {{cog|my|နွေး||warm; lukewarm}}, {{m|my|နွှေး||to warm something; to revise}}.

Often considered to be related to {{och-l|爇|to burn; to toast}} and {{och-l|焫|hot}}.

